"title": "3284: Holy Spirit, resisting",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "3284: holy spirit, resisting",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The work of the Holy Spirit can be resisted through disobedience and unbelief.</p>\n<h2>Scriptural images of resisting the Holy Spirit</h2>\n<h3>Grieving the Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa63:10\">ISA 63:10</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:30\">EPH 4:30</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Resisting the Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:51\">ACT 7:51</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:3\">GEN 6:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:9-Acts6:10\">ACT 6:9–6:10</a></p>\n<h3>Blaspheming against the Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:29\">MRK 3:29</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:31\">MAT 12:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:10\">LUK 12:10</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:29\">HEB 10:29</a></p>\n<h3>Quenching the Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:19\">1TH 5:19</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Lying to the Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:3\">ACT 5:3</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Testing the Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:9\">ACT 5:9</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Ways in which the Holy Spirit is resisted</h2>\n<h3>Through sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:17\">GAL 5:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:30-Eph4:31\">EPH 4:30–4:31</a></p>\n<h3>Through rebellion</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:33\">PSA 106:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa63:10\">ISA 63:10</a></p>\n<h3>Through hardness of heart</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech7:12\">ZEC 7:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:51\">ACT 7:51</a></p>\n<h3>Through spiritual blindness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:14\">1CO 2:14</a></strong></p>",
